      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been maintained with an emphasis on performance longevity, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its signature balance with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, offering precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, pulling hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key driver's car for the serious automotive purist.",
